104
00:06:21,330 --> 00:06:22,320
Koneko!

105
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,170
Ano!

106
00:06:23,170 --> 00:06:27,880
Věčný Budha k tobě bude milosrdný!

107
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:30,370
Budeme vás krýt!

108
00:06:30,370 --> 00:06:31,840
Rychle, utečte!

109
